QuestData.Title: Raucous Rousing
QuestData.Description: You ready for this, $n? I'm thinking maybe we should have looked for something to cover our ears, but it's a bit late for that now. Just remember that the intense ringing you'll be hearing for the next few hours is the ringing sound of victory!$B$BThe honor's all yours, $n. Ring the gong whenever you're ready!
